Package org.eclipse.persistence.platform.xml.jaxp

Class JAXPParser

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.persistence.platform.xml.jaxp.JAXPParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
XMLParser
public class JAXPParser extends Object implements XMLParser

Purpose: An implementation of XMLParser using JAXP 1.3 APIs.

JAXPParser is NOT thread safe.
